

                                       Screenshots and Listeners.class




  NOTE : - Intre "screenshots" si "Listeners" este o relatie stransa.
           "Screenshot-ul" se face numai atunci cand testul esueaza.
         - calea pentru a vizualiza "Screenshot-urile" (se gaseste in folderul "screenshots" din radacina proiectului) 


......................................... Taking screenshots for failing Tests: ....................................................

    1. Create a listeners package under "src/main/java".
    2. Create a Listeners class under it and make it implement ITestListener interface (import: "import org.testng.ITestListener;").
        Add TestNG library if unable to resolve the errors.
    3. Select 'Source' menu in Eclipse IDE < Override/Implement Methods and select all the check boxes of ITestListerner.
    4. Create reusable method for taking screenshots in Base class with two parameters.
    5. Extend the Listeners class with Base class .
    6. Update the onTestFailure() method of Listeners class .
    7. Add the Listeners tags in testng.xml file.
    8. Make the driver of the Test Classes to global and public !!!! ( adica : "public WebDriver driver;" ).
    9. Intentionally fail a test and run the testng.xml file.

....................................................................................................................................



